)
(uuid "aab61acf-0cb0-492c-a6cf-a32d135b09fd")
)
(text "Mode button (momentary NO):\n  GPIO14 -- BTN -- GND\n  GPIO14 = INPUT_PULLUP\n  Optional: 100nF across button\n\nConnector detect:\n  J_MAIN pin1 (3V3_SENSE)\n   -- 10k --> GPIO9 (INPUT_PULLDOWN)\n  Plugged=HIGH, Removed=LOW\n\nMain power switch:\n  Hardware latching switch in series\n  with LiPo -> TP4056 - no GPIO needed"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 3 178 0)
(effects
(font
(size 1 1)
)
(justify left top)
)
(uuid "a83c3638-2c00-4cc0-8d93-1d35f1b48b69")
)

(text "BLOCK 9 - J_MAIN (20-PIN INSOLE CONNECTOR)"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 273 3 0)
(effects
(font
(size 1.5 1.5)
(bold yes)
)
(justify left)
)
(uuid "0260b674-ffec-40bb-9192-8b36f4311ec0")
)
(text "Pin  Net           Dir\n  1  3V3_SENSE     -> insole (connector detect)\n  2  5V_SYS        -> insole\n  3  GND\n  4  GND           (duplicate return)\n  5  FSR1_RAW      <- sensor\n  6  FSR2_RAW      <- sensor\n  7  FSR3_RAW      <- sensor\n  8  FSR4_RAW      <- sensor\n  9  ACT1_OA1      -> coil\n 10  ACT1_OA2      -> coil\n 11  ACT1_OB1      -> coil\n 12  ACT1_OB2      -> coil\n 13  ACT2_OA1      -> coil\n 14  ACT2_OA2      -> coil\n 15  ACT2_OB1      -> coil\n 16  ACT2_OB2      -> coil\n 17  ACT3_OA1      -> coil\n 18  ACT3_OA2      -> coil\n 19  ACT3_OB1      -> coil\n 20  ACT3_OB2      -> coil\n\nDual GND pins mandatory for motor return current\nConnector: IDC / Molex / screw terminal"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 273 6 0)
(effects
(font
(size 1 1)
)
(justify left top)
)
(uuid "0edcae7a-5f97-4e95-96f5-6fa75e94c2ec")
)

(text "PIN MAP - DO NOT CHANGE WITHOUT LAYOUT REVIEW"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 115 195 0)
(effects
(font
(size 1.5 1.5)
(bold yes)
)
(justify left)
)
(uuid "6be24a52-9a88-498e-8dc1-78e7fa444b6f")
)
(text "GPIO0  = FSR1_METATARSAL (ADC)\nGPIO1  = FSR2_ARCH (ADC)\nGPIO2  = FSR3_CALCANEUS (ADC)\nGPIO3  = FSR4_AUX (ADC)\nGPIO4  = STEPPER_ENN (active LOW)\nGPIO5  = VBAT_SENSE (ADC - 1:2 divider)\nGPIO6  = ACT1_STEP\nGPIO7  = ACT1_DIR\nGPIO9  = CONN_DETECT (INPUT_PULLDOWN)\nGPIO12 = ACT2_STEP\nGPIO13 = ACT2_DIR\nGPIO14 = MODE_BUTTON (INPUT_PULLUP)\nGPIO20 = ACT3_STEP\nGPIO21 = ACT3_DIR\nGPIO22 = OLED_SDA\nGPIO23 = OLED_SCL\nAVOID: GPIO8 (RGB LED)  GPIO10/11 (not broken out)\n       GPIO15 (boot strap)  USB pins"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 115 198 0)
(effects
(font
(size 1 1)
)
(justify left top)
)
(uuid "f6376d85-5630-4592-8aa3-07cedefeed90")
)

(text "ENGINEERING NOTES"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 273 195 0)
(effects
(font
(size 1.5 1.5)
(bold yes)
)
(justify left)
)
(uuid "fa9ba984-5a8f-4dba-925b-a5b00189dfa7")
)
(text "POWER:\n  ESP32 powered from 5V_SYS ONLY - never directly from LiPo\n  Charging and actuation MUTUALLY EXCLUSIVE\n  Firmware disables STEPPER_ENN on USB/charge detect\n\nLAYOUT (single-layer PCB - jumpers allowed):\n  Zone A (LEFT):   LiPo, TP4056, XL6009, bulk caps\n  Zone B (CENTRE): TMC2209, motor output traces\n  Zone C (RIGHT):  ESP32, FSR, OLED - farthest from boost\n  NEVER route motor return current through analog ground\n  Trunk+branch ground topology (battery-neg = origin)\n\nTRACE WIDTHS:\n  Power/GND: 1.5-2.0mm   Motor: 0.8-1.2mm\n  Digital: 0.25-0.4mm    Analog/I2C: 0.25-0.4mm\n\nFIRMWARE RULES:\n  Never start all 3 motors simultaneously (stagger 50-100ms)\n  Sample FSR only when motors idle or use median filter x5\n  OLED update rate <= 10Hz during actuation\n  Expose PDN_UART and DIAG pads per TMC2209\n  USB port on ESP32 and TP4056 must remain accessible"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 273 198 0)
(effects
(font
(size 1 1)
)
(justify left top)
)
(uuid "e0492219-99b1-4080-aa57-44118eded0fb")
)

(text "PASSIVES CHECKLIST"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 3 235 0)
(effects
(font
(size 1.5 1.5)
(bold yes)
)
(justify left)
)
(uuid "27cc0328-8ddf-40a6-975d-641a690f0450")
)
(text "XL6009 output:\n  [ ] 470uF 35V electrolytic\n  [ ] 470-1000uF 35V electrolytic (extra)\n  [ ] 100nF ceramic\nESP32 3V3 supply:\n  [ ] 10uF\n  [ ] 100nF ceramic\nPer TMC2209 x3:\n  [ ] 100uF electrolytic on VM\n  [ ] 100nF ceramic on VM\n  [ ] 100nF ceramic on VIO\nFSR front-end x4:\n  [ ] 10k pull-down\n  [ ] 1k series\n  [ ] 100nF at ADC pin\nBattery sense:\n  [ ] 100k + 100k divider\nUser interface:\n  [ ] 10k pull-down for CONN_DETECT\n  [ ] Optional 100nF across mode button"
(exclude_from_sim no)
(at 3 238 0)
(effects
